				offline media			








				A different kind of media.			



This is not offline media as you think of it today. It’s not just signage or print ads, it’s connecting and building your Brand where your target is engaged and receptive. And it’s authentic, never forced.



























  branding			




 








				Customizable, high impact branding where your consumers are looking and participating.			



Want dominant brand messaging where a high volume of your target consumers are present? Look no further than our proprietary high school platform. Here you can showcase your Brand and drive to a community location (if desired), all at the same time.





















Branded field level signage, close to the action, gets noticed throughout events













Branded PA announcements capture the audience’s attention at breaks in the action













In-school branded banners and posters in high traffic areas, (main office, counseling center, gym and cafeteria) reach high numbers of teens













Branded print ads & inserts in game programs or distributed as flyers get 1/1 attention













Branded “beauty books” can feature anything from recipes and coupons to service benefits













Branded keeper pieces, like annual “home game” schedule magnets that are 1/1 distributed













Branded feather flags and goal posts













Branded field or floor decals





























