				Drive engagement and traffic through promotions.			



Drive consumer activity and engagement through creative promotions and valuable incentives. Sweepstakes and contests offer a campaign overlay that enables Brands to excite different consumer segments.





















Coupon distribution via school “keeper piece” (e.g., the annual football schedule)













QR codes and mobile tie-ins incent engagement and allow data capture for re-contact













Text-to-win promotions keep consumers engaged for a longer period of time













Contests & sweepstakes can drive engagement of parents and teens













Distribution of branded promotional cards at events call further attention to active contests





























