Company Overview of Offline Media Inc



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Offline Media Inc, develops an online platform where users can discover people, places, things to do through group events, and how to spend their money and time. It also leverages users LinkedIn profile to create an event platform for professionals. The company was founded in 2012 and is based in Raleigh, North Carolina with additional offices in Nashville, Tennessee.


